p.k: The Wattersons are surprised to discover that their past actions have consequences. / The life of the background objects of Elmore are shown in a series of short skits. / The Watterson kids come up with a fool-proof plan. / Gumball accidentally uploads a video of himself and wants it gone. / Gumball and Darwin's reputation is challenged and they really couldn't care less... / Gumball and Darwin fail to make some instant homemade movie classics. / Richard is left in charge for the day, but his lack of rules attracts unwanted guests to the Watterson house. / Gumball and Darwin try to understand Juke's urgent beatbox message. / Gumball and Darwin must apologise to everyone they know after getting a threatening message on Elmore Plus.
